  "description": "Per-prompt and session spend visibility for Claude Code. See exactly what each prompt costs the moment it finishes — spot expensive prompts and spend leaks before you hit the 'usage limit' wall. Costs shown in USD or INR (live rate, auto-refreshes every 30 days).",
